<li>Fixed style missing issue for some components when imported on demand</li>
<li>Fixed disabled filterable multiple Select still showing dropdown when clicked on a certain area, #2540</li>
<li>Restored returning to original sorting in sortable Table columns, #2491</li>
<li>Added <code>reset.css</code> in <code>theme-default</code>, #2378</li>
<li>Added <code>range-separator</code> attribute for DatePicker, #2579</li>
<li>Published individual component packages: Table, DatePicker, Loading, Upload and Carousel</li>
<li>Add Finnish (@groenroos)</li>
</ul>
